{"id":288953,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-安徽芜湖等维权人士到南通呼吁释放冯兰/","date":"2013-04-13T22:46:25Z","modified":"2013-04-13T22:46:25Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽芜湖等维权人士到南通呼吁释放冯兰美（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，安徽芜湖维权人士周琛、朱小红和王瑞和济南倪文华赶到南通，与如皋冯兰美的女儿及其南通维权人士单利华等一起到南通市政府要求释放冯兰美。南通市信访局王局长说，为了冯兰美的事，王局长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>特地到南通跑了一趟。但没有告知跑了一趟有什么作用，等于白说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯兰美是江苏省如皋市拆迁户，因房屋被如城镇人民政府偷拆而向法院提起行政诉讼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，如皋市法院受理此案，仅隔了一天，如城镇政府将她关进黑监狱达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>天。冯兰美出来后，再次到北京上访，揭露被关黑监狱期间，政府逼她签订拆迁安置协议；如皋法院法官马跃逼她撤诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，如皋公安局崔叶和等将冯兰美从北京截访到如皋，关押至今。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-t27r-TWJz-E/UWmDO6d-y9I/AAAAAAAAgUY/_KHKztTfheM/s1600/DSCN2654.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"245\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-t27r-TWJz-E/UWmDO6d-y9I/AAAAAAAAgUY/_KHKztTfheM/s1600/DSCN2654.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_pos